attributes.title: This app is BROKEN AND DISGUSTING
attributes.review: I downloaded this app to see updates about trump and all his speeches only to be met with a part where it says to put my phone number in. When I put mine in it didn’t even do anything and I spent an entire hour on YouTube trying to figure out why! When I “found” a solution it glitched the ENTIRE app! Kicking me out and lagging my phone everytime I got in! Then my phone overheated and I had to pay 200 DOLLARS TO REPARE IT! I DO NOT! AND I REPEAT DO NOT RECOMMEND THIS APP TO ANY PEOPLE WANTING TO DOWNLOAD IT! IT WILL BREAK YOUR PHONE AND LEAVE YOU NO CHOICE TO BUY A REPLACEMENT OR REPAIR FOR HUNDREDS OF DOLLARS! I am SO dissatisfied with my purchase. The app is atrocious! DO NOT BUY UNLESS YOU WANT YOUR PHONE TO BREAK!
